, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in common,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "generally,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "universally, within the compass of its influence,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "effects"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S, TA.) So in the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saHaAbN yujal~ilu AlA^aroDa biAlmaTari", "text_ar": "سَحَابٌ يُجَلِّلُ الاَرْضَ بِالمَطَرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Clouds that include the land in common,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "generally,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "universally, within the compass of their rain;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that rain upon the land throughout its general,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "universal, extent"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S, TA:) or, as in the A,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thundering clouds, covering the land with rain."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And so in the phrase,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jal~ala AlmaTaru AlA^aroDa", "text_ar": "جَلَّلَ المَطَرُ الاَرْضَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The rain included the general,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "universal, extent of the land within the compass of its fall;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "covered the land so as not to leave anything uncovered."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IF, Msb.) ―         -b2-  And hence, [in a general sense,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He covered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a thing. (Msb.)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ascended, rose, mounted, got, was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, upon,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "over,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a thing; (Ham p. 45;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tajl~l", "text_ar": "تَجلّل", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, K.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He clad"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a horse (S, K) or beast (K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jul~", "text_ar": "جُلّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "covering for protection from the cold"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (S, K;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jal~a", "text_ar": "جَلَّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "TA", "K"]}, {"entry_id": "n6024", "headword_ar": "جَلَلٌ", "root": "jl", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A great, momentous,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "formidable, thing, affair, matter, case,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "event;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jul~aY", "text_ar": "جُلَّى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jul~aA='u", "text_ar": "جُلَّا=ءُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) or ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "julaY", "text_ar": "جُلَى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalalN", "text_ar": "جَلَلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jul~aA='u", "text_ar": "جُلَّا=ءُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a hard, difficult, severe,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distressing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a great, momentous,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "formidable, thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "affair,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.: (Msb:) pl. [of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalalN", "text_ar": "جَلَلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajolaAlN", "text_ar": "اَجْلَالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (TA;) and of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "julalN jul~aY", "text_ar": "جُلَلٌ جُلَّى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, K.) El-Hárith Ibn-Waaleh says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "qawomiY humu qataluwA A^umayoma A^axiY\n                      \n                     \n                        faA_i*aA ramayotu yuSiybuniY sahomiY\n                      \n                     \n                        falay^ino Eafawotu laA^aEofuwano jalalFA\n                      \n                     \n                        walay^ino saTwotu laA^uwohinano EaZomiY"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "My people, they have slain, O Umeymeh,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^umayoma", "text_ar": "اُمَيْمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "being apocopated, for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^umayomapu", "text_ar": "اُمَيْمَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "my brother; so, if I shoot, my arrow will strike me; and verily, if I forgive, I shall indeed forgive a great thing; but verily, if I assault, I shall indeed weaken my bone:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "see Ham p. 97]. (S.) And Beshámeh Ibn-Hazn says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "wamakorumapF ↓ \n      waA_ino daEawota A_ilaY jul~aY\n                      \n                     \n                        yawomFA saraApF kiraAma Aln~aAsi faA@doEiynaA"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And if thou invite to a great affair, and a generous act, any day, manly and noble persons, the generous of mankind, invite us"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jul~aY", "text_ar": "جُلَّى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is here an inf. n. in the place of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalaAlN", "text_ar": "جَلَالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalaAlapN", "text_ar": "جَلَالَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rujoEaY", "text_ar": "رُجْعَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", &c. (Ham p. 218.) ―         -b2-  Also, i. e.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalalN", "text_ar": "جَلَلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A small,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an easy,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a mean, paltry,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contemptible, thing, affair, matter, case,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "event:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA:) thus bearing two contr. significations. (S, K.) Imra-el-Keys says, on the occasion of his father's having been slain,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "A^alaA kul~u $aYo'K siwaAhu jalalo \n                      \n                     \n                        bi qatoli baniY A^asadK rab~ahumN"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "By Benoo-Asad's slaying their lord: now surely everything beside it is"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a mean, paltry,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "small, matter."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faEalotu *`lika mino", "text_ar": "فَعَلْتُ ذٰلِكَ مِنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalalika", "text_ar": "جَلَلِكَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I did that on account of thee, for thy sake,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"k